Lot of XMLs use namespaces so it would be very useful for me (and for others as well)?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14473638" author="stigat" created="Mon, 10 Dec 2012 13:56:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I would also find a fix for this very useful&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14480075" author="paulk" created="Fri, 21 Dec 2012 01:01:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed with a slight variation to your proposal since in XML the URI is the important thing not the prefix, hence the following assert would also work for your example:&lt;/p&gt;
